    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler G11N SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler G11N SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 The SIG aims to accelerate the globalization of openEuler and make openEuler ubiquitously accessible to people of all language backgrounds.。该 SIG 共有 6 名核心成员，维护 2 个代码仓库，属于 基础设施与工具 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler G11N SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler G11N SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 openeuler/G11N、openeuler/globalization）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 g11n@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler G11N SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler G11N SIG 共维护 2 个代码仓库，主要包括：openeuler/G11N、openeuler/globalization 等。完整列表见 https://www.openeuler.org/zh/sig/G11N。"
        }
      },
